headline: This Invesco ETF Pays a 4.71% Yield With 50 Low-Volatility Dividend Stocks (3x the S&P 500)
summary: Invesco High Dividend Low Volatility ETF (NYSEARCA:SPHD) generates its 4.71% yield – roughly three times the S&P 500’s current dividend – by holding a concentrated portfolio of 50 U.S. stocks selected for high dividend yields and low volatility.
